The company in a notification on Wednesday through the Nigerian Exchange Group to investing community which was endorsed by Samuel Ogbodu, Managing Director/CEO of the company said Chief Financial Officer, Mr Akeem Adamson and Company Secretary, Head of Legal and Chief Compliance Officer, Mr John Akujieze has resigned from the service of the company both effective 7th September 2021. The resignations were presented and had been accepted by the board of directors said the statement. On that note, Sunu Assurances Nigeria Plc board had approved the appointment of Mr Theo Lyile for CFO and Mrs Taiwo Kuku in acting capacity Company Secretary respectively pending final resolution in this regard. 